Types of private flights

If you want to charter a business for flying to/from Biggin Hill, Private Jets will be happy to help you with that. Our fleet includes thousands of proven jets with excellent performance, perfectly suitable for business flights.

Private Jets can arrange any type of flights, including:

Corporate flights. Corporate flights are especially popular with the heads of large corporations who want to send their staff on business trips, seminars or collective vacations;

Business flights. This option is popular with the managers of large companies who need to travel to/from Great Britain for partners’ meetings, deal-making or branch inspections. Business jets are equipped with satellite communication, Internet, meeting rooms and conference rooms;

Romantic flights. This is a perfect option for newlyweds, romantic couples or married couples who want to celebrate their wedding or wedding anniversary. A cosy atmosphere and comfortable furniture are especially important for such passengers. We can also arrange a buffet or deliver delicious meals from restaurants onboard;

Medical flights. Such flights are arranged for transporting seriously ill patients to a facility in another city or state in the shortest possible time. Medical flights are accompanied by health workers or a team of doctors and have special equipment on board. In this case, it is important to choose the business jet with the low vibration;

Freight flight. This type of flight is intended for the safe transportation of fragile and valuable items. In this case, the jet is selected based on the weight of equipment transported.

Private Jets UK provides services for VIPs, sports teams and dance groups. In addition, we transport teams of workers to hard-to-reach areas and perform corporate flights.

